                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17910914-56-off349 t17910914-56-cd350"></join>, one copper saucepan, value 6 d. a tin saucepan, value 1 d. one iron hammer, with a wooden handle, value 1 d. an iron fire shovel, value 4 d. a poker, value 4 d. a flat iron, value 4 d.
            </rs> the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t17910914-56-victim609" type="victimName">
